channel.title: Christmas List
channel.description: What are some things I should ask for christmas. Please don't post silly Ideas. I'm probably going to get another xbox 360 since mine broke. But there's alot more things to add to my list. WTF do I ask for? whats some fun shit to have so I don't get bored? thanks.
